'''''Valiant''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] armored [[Transport/Legends|transport]] ship. [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Stormtroopers]] were asking if anyone had heard of this ship in the [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina/Legends|Mos Eisley Cantina]] when [[Sithless Leethe]] was selling the ''[[Limping Lady]]'' to a group of wannabe [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]].<ref name="Limping Lady">{{ChallengeCite|64|Limping Lady}}</ref>

